# Whitelist approach: ignore everything by default, only track skill/task logic (.md), never business data or credentials
*
!*/
!*.md
!*.md.bak*
!.gitignore

# Extra safety: never track these even if matched above
*.pem
*.key
*.env
.env*
credentials*
*credential*
brevo_api_key
*.p12
*.pfx

# Explicit hard excludes: personal health data and financial/tax planning docs — never in git, regardless of extension
Projects/Health Optimization/
Projects/Quickbooks Set UP/
tools/
